headline: DoorDash Taps 50 Cent And Dining Rewards As Shares Lag Targets
summary: DoorDash has partnered with Curtis "50 Cent" Jackson for "The Big Beef" cultural campaign around the Big Game. The company is promoting its delivery offerings through content tied to the event and 50 Cent's brand. DoorDash is also expanding its Going Out rewards program ahead of Valentine’s Day. The updated program includes special perks and in app reservations at a range of restaurants.
